'''HomeKit''' 是[[苹果公司|苹果公司]]推出的一个[[软件框架|软件框架]]，它可以让用户使用苹果设备对智能家居电器进行配置、沟通和控制。通过在HomeKit服务中设计房间、物品和动作，用户可以通过对[[Siri|Siri]]的简单语音命令或通过家庭（Home）应用来实现家中的自动动作。<ref>{{cite web |first=Rene |last=Ritchie |authorlink=Rene Ritchie |title=HomeKit in iOS 8: Explained |url=http://www.imore.com/homekit-ios-8-explained |website=[[iMore|iMore]] |date=2014-08-27 |accessdate=2016-12-26 |archive-date=2016-12-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161226145924/http://www.imore.com/homekit-ios-8-explained |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==概述==
HomeKit使用[[蓝牙|蓝牙]]和[[Wi-Fi|Wi-Fi]]协议<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.tomsguide.com/us/apple-homekit-faq,review-4195.html|title=Apple HomeKit: What Is It, and How Do You Use It?|last=Chin|first=Monica|last2=Chang 2019-09-27T15:27:35Z|first2=Althea|website=Tom's Guide|language=en|access-date=2020-01-06|archive-date=2019-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191211010929/https://www.tomsguide.com/us/apple-homekit-faq,review-4195.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，支持HomeKit的设备制造商需要[[MFi认证|MFi认证]]<ref>{{cite web |title=Working with HomeKit |url=https://developer.apple.com/homekit/ |publisher=[[Apple_Inc.|Apple Inc.]] |accessdate=December 26, 2016 |archive-date=2017-01-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170105043219/https://developer.apple.com/homekit/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，最初所有基于HomeKit的产品都需要包含一个加密协处理器<ref>{{cite web |first=Stacey |last=Higginbotham |title=What one startup CEO learned from handling Apple's HomeKit mess |url=http://fortune.com/2015/06/09/ceo-apple-homekit-mess/ |website=[[Fortune_(magazine)|Fortune]] |publisher=[[Time_Inc.|Time Inc.]] |date=June 10, 2015 |accessdate=December 26, 2016 |archive-date=2017-02-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170202111815/http://fortune.com/2015/06/09/ceo-apple-homekit-mess/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但在iOS11之后，HomeKit增加了对软件认证的支持<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.imore.com/how-homekits-software-authentication-works|title=How HomeKit's software authentication works|date=29 March 2018|accessdate=2020-07-16|archive-date=2020-08-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200801195205/https://www.imore.com/how-homekits-software-authentication-works|dead-url=no}}</ref>，没有HomeKit支持的设备可以通过“网关”使用，閘道器是连接这些设备和HomeKit服务的桥梁
。<ref>{{cite web |first1=Thomas |last1=Ricker |first2=Jacob |last2=Kastrenakes |title=First HomeKit devices confirm Apple TV's limited role in home automation |url=https://www.theverge.com/2015/1/8/7510647/first-homekit-devices-confirm-apple-tvs-role-in-home-automation |website=[[The_Verge|The Verge]] |publisher=[[Vox_Media|Vox Media]] |date=January 8, 2015 |accessdate=December 26, 2016 |archive-date=2016-12-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161222082055/http://www.theverge.com/2015/1/8/7510647/first-homekit-devices-confirm-apple-tvs-role-in-home-automation |dead-url=no }}</ref>

HomeKit主要与[[亚马逊公司|亚马逊公司]]和[[谷歌|谷歌]]的[[智能家居|智能家居]]标准竞争，截至2019年10月，苹果列出了450款兼容HomeKit的设备，而谷歌和亚马逊的设备分别为1万和8.5万。

